title: Versetti for Organ by Anonymous Masters on Schnitger Organ, Eenu
description:
Versetti in the 8 toni  

by anonymous masters

The manuscript of the Archive of the Minoritenkonvent, Vienna.

World premiere recording

The works may had been written around 1650, the collection was created for the purposes of the court chapel, Vienna.
